Download SCons (new version).

    wget http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/scons/scons-local-4.3.0.zip

Unpack (new version dir).

    unzip scons-local-4.3.0.zip -d _tmp_scons

Inspect contents.

	$ tree _tmp_scons -L 3 -F --dirsfirst
	_tmp_scons/
	├── scons-local-4.3.0/
