Defaults need Scanner parts and Tool.

    cp _tmp_scons/scons-local-4.3.0/SCons/Scanner/Dir.py .scons/SCons/Scanner

    mkdir .scons/SCons/Tool
    cp _tmp_scons/scons-local-4.3.0/SCons/Tool/__init__.py .scons/SCons/Tool

Tool unconditionally imports Scanner.C and a bunch of others (patchable). Maybe
it is possible to create delayed import.

    # commented all unconditionally imported tools

